This is a comparitively small Deathrun map with only 6 traps
The Levels Go like:
- Normal Push and kill level
- Explosion
- Fire
Then The level 2 Consists of
- Break Floor Trap
- 2 ledge Trap
- Long Jump Map
**Sorry for the poor style of maps, it is my first map and I will try my best to Improve in  my way of making maps and will do my best in contributing in the creation of maps.  **
This map Can be played with 25cts and one T
